snippet: Washington Nationals reliever Aaron Barrett, who is recovering from Tommy John surgery, said his elbow problems had stemmed from overuse.
abstract: Washington Nationals pitcher Aaron Barrett, currently recovering from Tommy John surgery, blames his elbow problems on overuse.
